page.title: 17PEOPLE OF STRATHNAIRN
page.content: {Length of stay}Only three families in this area had ancestors here.2 have lived here for more than 30 years,6 between 10 and 30,4 between 5 and 10,5 between 1 and 5 and 5 less than a year. {Origin}Before they moved here 10 families lived more than 50 miles away,2 between 10 and 50 miles and 10 upto 10 miles away. {Employment}There are 5 retired people living in this area,3 people work from home,8 work in Strathnairn and 10 work in Inverness. {Occupations}We have a nurse,3 farmers, a company director,a gamekeeper,a gardener,an insurance broker,a fencer, a sub_post mistress,a minister,a lecturer,a law officer,a sales executive,a council worker,a civil servant,2 teachers,a caretaker,a secretary and the head of the H.I.D.B.
